
  Blaziken    Fire Type Pokémon

  In battle, BLAZIKEN blows out 
  intense flames from its wrists 
  and attacks foes courageously. 
   The stronger the foe, the more 
  intensely Blaziken’s wrists 
  burn. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Torchic ► Combusken ► Blaziken

